data.description: Charming two story home on a corner lot inviting you to come and experience the cozy, open floor plan featuring hard laminate and tile flooring, three great size bedrooms and two and a half bath. Come and see this newer home in a mature neighborhood with lots of light and character that is surely not to disappoint. Home sits on a large corner lot so there is room to spare! Schedule your showing soon and see how you can make this house your home today. Great opportunities like this dont last long, call it home today.
